Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.96,0:00:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是大植物园啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.20,0:00:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.95,0:00:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.59,0:00:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.45,0:00:48.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.12,0:00:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 遥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.01,0:00:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要了 都已经不是那个年龄了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.89,0:00:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.87,0:01:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要约会的话 还是这样好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.29,0:01:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是成熟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.12,0:01:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸不也是被搭讪了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 看见了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.17,0:01:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.49,0:01:09.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没什么事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.53,0:01:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是被她询问了一下观光的地方而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.32,0:01:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 是个美人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.24,0:01:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.32,0:01:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.70,0:02:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(460,320)\fad(300,0)\bord0\be1\1c&Hdca561&}\N香\N\N格\N\N里\N\N拉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.87,0:02:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在这里行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.75,0:02:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 因为我喜欢这里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.92,0:03:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.63,0:03:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥来游乐园能开心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.41,0:03:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.47,0:03:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.12,0:03:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还在东京的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.69,0:03:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到外婆家时在暑假的时候一起去过不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.48,0:03:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你记得还真清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.90,0:03:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为现在住的阿婆的房子里 也是大家一起住着的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.02,0:03:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.17,0:03:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候大家一起来这个游乐园了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.20,0:03:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.03,0:03:43.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在怨恨爸爸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.85,0:03:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.81,0:03:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...只是在谈快乐的回忆而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.63,0:03:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.04,0:03:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.70,0:04:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我成人以后 这里还会在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.34,0:04:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥 最近是不是又见到幽灵了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.67,0:04:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽灵？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.75,0:04:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时侯 你不是因为一直看到幽灵而哭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.93,0:04:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那个啊 其实不是幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.55,0:04:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.89,0:04:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 黛博士 我正找你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.63,0:04:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换手机号码了的话 也该告诉我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.58,0:04:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说要再一次好好谈一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.03,0:04:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在和女儿在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.79,0:04:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是好久不见的再会吧 就尽情享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.23,0:04:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才十二岁的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.27,0:04:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候碰上交通事故不是不可能的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.39,0:04:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是让人担心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.91,0:04:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被母亲剥夺抚养权的父亲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.60,0:04:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.77,0:04:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候见面好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.49,0:05:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地点在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.08,0:05:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么两个小时后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.20,0:05:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥 爸爸...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.05,0:05:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.09,0:05:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 现在不马上回饭店的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.41,0:05:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的 路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.16,0:05:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.76,0:05:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.86,0:05:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过作为补偿 下次我去东京看你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.35,0:05:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东京？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.43,0:05:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经可以一个人去了 东京
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.70,0:05:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候 这次的份也要算上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.96,0:05:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 不要这样推我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.18,0:06:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天爸爸给你买了什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.36,0:06:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊 突然来了工作的电话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.91,0:06:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就马上回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:13.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎~ 难得来看女儿的说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.54,0:06:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.05,0:06:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次见面的时候 一定要算上这次的份好好买一下东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.93,0:06:21.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是就是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.79,0:06:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥 遥 鸢不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.62,0:06:29.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 鸢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.26,0:06:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是去散步了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.85,0:06:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦也不在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.72,0:06:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燕雀 不要摆出一副寂寞的表情嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.68,0:06:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃吃这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.08,0:06:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 美保
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.52,0:06:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 啪塔啪塔 都洒掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.38,0:06:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴边也都脏了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.61,0:06:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得美保很中意燕雀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.31,0:07:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是在这附近呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显示出时空的歪曲 鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.92,0:07:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.48,0:07:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 鸢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.39,0:07:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦 发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.69,0:07:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.86,0:07:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还是孩子的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.29,0:07:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信时间的流向从过去到未来是不会改变的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.62,0:07:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.84,0:07:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前 大家都只是太无知了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.54,0:07:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 时间这个概念却不是人类实行的社会制度那么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.97,0:07:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相却是给予空间和连锁变动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.43,0:07:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:43.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我们知道 无论时间还是空间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.58,0:07:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是一直在变化的 不确定的东西时
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.62,0:07:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类不就是失去了自身的存在意义了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.89,0:07:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论是这个时空 还是拉库利玛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.09,0:07:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有我 遥也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.17,0:08:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许一切都只不过是个幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.15,0:08:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是不正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.08,0:08:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据观测 存在是可以被确认的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.74,0:08:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦找到了遥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.94,0:08:13.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以遥存在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.35,0:08:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 遥也找到了鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.47,0:08:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以鸦才会在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.04,0:08:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝山上跑 你准备干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.87,0:08:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正试着把量子形式数值化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.19,0:08:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做这样的事能让那些家伙承认吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.23,0:08:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想委员会是不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.65,0:08:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 黛博士的话 一定会明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.24,0:08:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊 你不是连那个博士在哪都不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士肯定在遥那里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.15,0:08:56.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.26,0:08:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.44,0:08:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.69,0:09:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郡山先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.16,0:09:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内田 你待在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.57,0:09:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 郡山先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.97,0:09:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.24,0:09:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在这里做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.27,0:09:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.65,0:09:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是员警
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.15,0:09:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有些事情想问你们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.43,0:09:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郡山先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.07,0:09:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 不可能语言不通吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.66,0:09:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.35,0:09:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说了给我到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.06,0:09:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.27,0:09:42.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 不过是魔术罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.10,0:09:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这闷热的午间还穿着什么斗篷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.57,0:09:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.51,0:09:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听了也是无用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.56,0:09:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是无法理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.78,0:10:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记吧 然后快点离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.32,0:10:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行 你以为你在逗小孩玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.31,0:10:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不好好说明的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.38,0:10:08.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.01,0:10:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.66,0:10:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是十年后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.36,0:10:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时空如果再过十年
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.34,0:10:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就能理解我的存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.08,0:10:23.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装预言家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.40,0:10:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再让我仔细听听吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.25,0:10:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在装有铁栅栏窗户的房间里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.59,0:10:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.15,0:10:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是 定位时空中的定位存在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.70,0:10:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,判定量子立场和时空相对性的边界的世界对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得那些说明对鸦来说实在太复杂了些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.19,0:10:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你前面的话 说的很对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.45,0:10:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 你很优秀哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.62,0:10:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你的话 说不定能理解我们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.06,0:10:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.65,0:11:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 勇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.66,0:11:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.33,0:11:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是糟糕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.98,0:11:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.47,0:11:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.56,0:11:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她好像拥有不可思议的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.61,0:11:13.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 突然说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.39,0:11:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么不可思议的力量 不要说不着边际的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.75,0:11:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是啊 鸦也对我说了 让我保护遥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.87,0:11:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的是啊 我们可是男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.49,0:11:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就必须保护女人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.86,0:11:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.56,0:11:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇有喜欢的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.42,0:11:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 那是当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.59,0:11:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连喜欢的女人都没有一个怎么行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.74,0:11:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 有啊 谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.82,0:11:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.71,0:11:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是秘密哦 佑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.26,0:11:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪绘老师？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.58,0:11:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 怎么会 不要出那么大声啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.63,0:11:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事情大家都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.87,0:11:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.50,0:11:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.24,0:11:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问勇这个问题的我才是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.84,0:11:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 佑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.93,0:11:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.51,0:12:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.52,0:12:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.60,0:12:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是魔术吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.03,0:12:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是这附近很异常
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.47,0:12:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有歪曲的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.46,0:12:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.22,0:12:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在那里面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.13,0:12:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在那里面有反应 鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.81,0:12:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.50,0:12:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么走 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.90,0:12:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.32,0:12:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 内田
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.56,0:12:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.30,0:12:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是的 又掉到水里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.42,0:12:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎都没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.37,0:12:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.54,0:12:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 这个怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.59,0:12:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了 爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.92,0:12:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样做怎么能够妨碍到我的水道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.34,0:12:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎~又是我的水道管
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.10,0:12:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美保好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.11,0:13:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱好差劲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.84,0:13:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 怎么了 燕雀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.80,0:13:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.42,0:13:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边也可以确认到反应
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.98,0:13:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 是非常微弱的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.04,0:13:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.24,0:13:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了微小的临界反应
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.09,0:13:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 有什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.19,0:13:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦 稍微过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.51,0:13:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.89,0:13:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这深处出现了不规则的震动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.18,0:13:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看见什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.63,0:13:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是正面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.99,0:13:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么也看不见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.95,0:13:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般是看不见的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.06,0:14:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是临界域
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.75,0:14:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,临界域？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.34,0:14:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 那个圆环
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.66,0:14:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是时空的连接域
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.12,0:14:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌罗波洛斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.09,0:14:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是乌罗波洛斯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.49,0:14:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 内田 危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.84,0:14:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 内田
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.45,0:14:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.75,0:14:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸢君 这是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.62,0:14:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个作为存在却还没有确定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.05,0:14:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.80,0:14:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照你们的科学水平来说 是量子形式的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.81,0:14:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不断叠加的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.37,0:14:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为存在却还没有确定的东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.75,0:14:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.26,0:14:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我看到的那个圆环难道是幻影吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.11,0:14:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是我自己出问题了 到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见 遥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.40,0:15:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.42,0:15:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燕雀 拜托你送她们了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.87,0:15:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去了 遥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.57,0:15:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.92,0:15:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做什么呢 遥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.51,0:15:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.39,0:15:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点出牌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.93,0:15:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在发呆了啊 这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.15,0:15:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.46,0:15:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸢君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.88,0:15:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道这圆环之后是...香格里拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.46,0:15:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香格里拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.63,0:15:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙..是香格里拉的假面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.25,0:15:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.38,0:15:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦 遥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.92,0:15:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥有危险
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.38,0:16:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是的 没有同样的卡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.97,0:16:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥 要阻止美保哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.78,0:16:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 不行的 不行的
