Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.32,0:16:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.74,0:16:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我让开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.41,0:17:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦
