Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.38,0:17:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退后 遥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.61,0:17:27.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.24,0:17:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来 遥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.66,0:17:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.18,0:17:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.59,0:17:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.98,0:17:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.80,0:17:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来 遥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.60,0:17:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴着假面的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.01,0:18:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥 我们一起走吧
